DE_Partyhouse

By SwampyTurtle
Helped by:  Mojo68
            CanMan


My first true map. it never felt right to release as a final map. Therefore i am releasing it as a MiP so that others may have a chance to mess around with it or make a final Version of it. If you decide to finish it please give me credit for the orginal work along with mentioning Mojo68 for his incredable help in getting me interested in hammer, thank you and enjoy
